WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:02.960
Hey, good morning family, praise the Lord.

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:04.285
Thank you for joining us.

00:00:04.285 --> 00:00:11.426
It's Diana and Brandon again, the dynamic duo.

00:00:11.426 --> 00:00:16.379
I'm excited to be here, baby.

00:00:16.379 --> 00:00:27.630
I have some things on my heart, and I know you do.

00:00:27.630 --> 00:00:36.353
We were talking about it today and what we feel in the atmosphere.

00:00:43.354 --> 00:00:56.834
You can feel there's a tangible feeling that something is about to happen, like a puzzle you just focus on and try to figure out all the pieces, and it's too hard.

00:00:57.869 --> 00:01:23.467
So you just have to focus on the piece that you have in your hand, praying that piece through instead of thinking about the whole, like, 'Well, this is overwhelming, all of this needs prayer.

00:01:23.467 --> 00:01:46.971
' You just focus on one piece at a time, the piece that's right in front of you, and you pray that through.

00:01:47.714 --> 00:02:20.480
And when that piece goes in and you see it go into the puzzle, then He'll hand you another piece and you just pray over that piece and you keep doing it until the whole picture's done.

00:02:20.480 --> 00:02:48.440
Sometimes we just get overwhelmed in prayer thinking about how this is a mess, this whole puzzle needs this, and I can't even see what it's going to be like.

00:02:48.440 --> 00:03:02.360
You don't even know what the picture is or where we are going right now.

00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:20.103
And that's where I felt like when I'm praying, I asked, 'What is priority number one, Lord, on Your heart?

00:03:20.103 --> 00:03:32.910
' Because right now the canvas she's talking about, this massive canvas, this puzzle, is overwhelming.

00:03:33.920 --> 00:04:09.450
I was praying over it, and I know that what I have right now, what I've seen in the spirit and what I saw in a video back, is another storm—a major shaking to awaken is coming, you all.

00:04:09.450 --> 00:04:35.631
After I stopped praying with you, I prayed for at least another hour, praying into that because the spirit of intercession hit me so hard.

00:04:38.627 --> 00:04:38.836
It was so heavy.

00:04:47.684 --> 00:04:51.540
I came in, sat on the couch, and I started hearing prophetically about our life.

00:04:53.554 --> 00:05:02.874
The Lord just started downloading again, warning us of what's coming.

00:05:09.084 --> 00:05:22.911
I saw a rectangular window before me in the spirit realm, and the Lord told me there is going to be a window of blessing.

00:05:28.440 --> 00:06:19.759
I'm telling you, you can see it right now, that what I saw about the economy crash is trying to manifest right in front of our faces, but the Lord is saying if we would pray and seek His face, He would give us this window of opportunity for the wealth of the wicked to be laid up for the righteous.

00:06:19.759 --> 00:06:34.125
We need this for the harvest; we need this wealth transfer.

00:06:34.125 --> 00:06:55.120
Listening to Him on a day-to-day basis, listening to Him on what to do with your finances, because God is going to be a rewarder of those that diligently seek Him.

00:07:07.599 --> 00:07:18.840
I don't believe it's for us to go into this crash of what I've seen coming with nothing and be there going, 'How are we going to do this?

00:07:18.840 --> 00:07:30.444
' I believe it's going to be a surplus on the body of Christ.

00:07:30.444 --> 00:07:42.893
For what I have seen, I told you, a remnant will walk in the blessing.

00:07:44.675 --> 00:07:54.279
I saw a one percent margin, and they go, 'Well, you know, that's not enough.

00:07:54.279 --> 00:08:02.035
' Well, one percent out of a billion is pretty good.

00:08:02.035 --> 00:08:10.528
I mean, I don't know, that's a lot of folks.

00:08:10.528 --> 00:08:23.182
I don't know the math on it exactly, but I'm just saying that's a lot.

00:08:23.182 --> 00:09:02.657
So I'm not going to say the sky is falling, but I've told you all, I have seen a major economic shaking that is worse than the 1920s or 1930s, worse than the Great Depression.

00:09:11.680 --> 00:09:12.060
It was the Great Depression on steroids.

00:09:12.060 --> 00:09:23.218
I'm talking very bad looting, rioting, and pillaging like we've never seen before.

00:09:23.218 --> 00:09:43.840
People act crazy because it's not like it was in the thirties; people have no morals like they did then, some common sense.

00:09:43.840 --> 00:09:49.306
I saw places of refuge again.

00:09:53.415 --> 00:09:55.500
The Lord spoke about places having water.

00:10:06.559 --> 00:10:06.906
I saw a great drought again.

00:10:08.293 --> 00:10:25.425
I saw great manipulation with the weather again, and I thought it was very interesting because I was watching Benny Johnson's video about the JFK files.

00:10:25.425 --> 00:10:46.188
My son, my wife, and I were all watching it, and we were like, 'Oh dear God,' at how corrupt the CIA was back in the sixties.

00:10:46.188 --> 00:11:26.160
It was overwhelming, really, some of the things that were being said and what he was reading in the transcripts from those 80,000-page reports about Israel, the nuclear capabilities, and setting up governments with all kinds of dirtiness.

00:11:26.160 --> 00:11:59.420
It was bad stuff; I was embarrassed as a citizen of the United States of America to hear that coming from our government, how corrupt they were even in the sixties.

00:12:05.009 --> 00:12:10.640
I was like, 'Wow, my dad was a little boy; this is really bad.

00:12:10.640 --> 00:12:17.532
' I'm just saying folks, it's eye-opening.

00:12:17.532 --> 00:12:38.987
And weather manipulation—they were using weather trying to figure out how to use weather manipulation to dethrone governments.

00:12:43.546 --> 00:12:48.280
This is what I've been praying over.

00:12:53.715 --> 00:13:17.360
I've told you all that they're going to use weather manipulation like we've never seen it before, and there will be drought in some areas and rain in another.

00:13:17.360 --> 00:13:29.959
It's going to be very serious drought and very serious floods.

00:13:29.959 --> 00:13:34.695
All that to say, I'm not afraid of it.

00:13:36.456 --> 00:13:39.149
I have total peace.

00:13:39.149 --> 00:13:56.394
Whenever people say, 'Are you tormented when you see these things?

00:13:56.394 --> 00:14:02.155
' No, I have total peace.

00:14:11.160 --> 00:14:11.440
I don't even let it get to me.

00:14:18.830 --> 00:14:21.813
I just go, 'This isn't about me; this is about a shaking.

00:14:21.813 --> 00:14:50.775
' If I let my flesh look at it in the natural, yeah, you could get freaked out, but I stay spiritual about it and I stay in the spirit, praying in tongues over it.

00:14:50.775 --> 00:15:12.916
When the Lord shows me the things to come and warns you about these things, it's not for me to sound the alarm in fear like 'Chicken Little, the sky is falling.

00:15:12.916 --> 00:15:35.851
' There's going to be a great economic crisis and people are going to stand in food lines for miles long.

00:15:48.840 --> 00:15:51.720
I'm saying it as a watchman seeing it, and I refuse to fear it because I have peace.

00:15:51.720 --> 00:16:22.569
You know when it's the Spirit of the Lord warning you about something versus the devil coming and tormenting you, it's when you have the peace that passes understanding while looking into something that should scare you, something that should make you crawl in a fetal position and rock.

00:16:22.569 --> 00:16:30.546
Does that freak me out right now when I'm telling you this?

00:16:30.546 --> 00:16:30.959
No.

00:16:30.959 --> 00:16:31.943
Why?

00:16:31.943 --> 00:16:39.839
Because I'm hearing the Spirit of the Lord warn me about something that's coming.

00:16:39.839 --> 00:16:57.650
When I see the plague and I see the people all on the cots, and I've seen all these things, was I in fear over that?

00:16:57.650 --> 00:17:13.949
No, not even a little bit, because I'm seeing it by the prophetic eye, the watchman eye.

00:17:13.949 --> 00:17:52.760
What the Lord's warned me about the plagues coming, I say none of that comes near me because He said if you stand on Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 and you get that down as a pillar in your heart, that no weapon formed against you will prosper.

00:17:52.760 --> 00:17:56.615
That's where we stay.

00:18:02.284 --> 00:18:16.213
We walk through the valley of the shadow of death, but we will fear no evil regardless of the plague, regardless of the pestilence.

00:18:16.524 --> 00:18:25.680
And the Lord showed me, He said, ' Brandon, America will be humbled.

00:18:25.680 --> 00:18:58.400
' That's not a word I want to tell everybody, but He said the church, the people, have a stiff neck towards Me, and in this, there will be a shaking to awaken again.

00:18:58.400 --> 00:19:17.900
I was looking at the hearts upon the land, and all of a sudden, all the hearts became one heart.

00:19:17.900 --> 00:19:38.480
It was very strange, but I could see all the hearts of the church and the nation, and all of them became one heart.

00:19:48.476 --> 00:19:55.069
The heart was black-looking and it had blood flowing from it.

00:20:00.740 --> 00:20:03.200
The center was starting to turn black.

00:20:12.537 --> 00:20:21.657
There was a little red left, but it was trying to turn into a black heart.

00:20:21.657 --> 00:20:26.160
What does that mean?

00:20:35.165 --> 00:20:35.531
I don't know.

00:20:35.531 --> 00:20:49.506
I see it and I pray over it, but it is alarming to me.

00:20:49.506 --> 00:21:11.271
It wasn't just one heart, one person; it was a vast majority of hearts, and it all became one heart.

00:21:15.305 --> 00:21:32.556
There was a little sliver of red in the middle, and all around it looked like it was toxic.

00:21:36.953 --> 00:22:31.886
The further it went out, it was black, and then it went into gray and then red.

00:22:31.886 --> 00:22:35.559
That's what I saw in the spirit.

00:23:25.440 --> 00:23:26.284
I haven't said that to anybody; even my family didn't know that.

00:23:26.284 --> 00:23:42.800
Some things I pray and I go, 'Oh, I probably should say that,' but that's what I saw.

00:23:42.800 --> 00:23:57.520
Then I saw the people with their noses stuck up and their necks were stiff.

00:23:57.520 --> 00:24:05.640
That's why I call them stiff-necked, because their necks were stiff.

00:24:05.640 --> 00:24:33.680
They were all upon the land and He said, 'A great humbling is coming,' but I'm giving you a window for My beloved, for My remnant, so that this will not affect you if you're listening to Me.

00:24:33.680 --> 00:24:40.337
If you remember, Abraham interceded on behalf of Lot.

00:24:40.337 --> 00:25:00.435
Lot did not know that judgment was coming because he was living there and he was amongst them.

00:25:00.435 --> 00:26:25.529
Because he had become lukewarm and become part of Sodom and Gomorrah in the way they thought, he did not know that in a 24-hour period judgment was coming.

00:26:25.529 --> 00:27:24.294
So God sent an angelic host to go and get Lot and his family out of that hellhole, and he grabbed a hold of them because of intercessory prayer.

00:27:24.294 --> 00:27:31.212
Abraham interceded on behalf of Lot.

00:27:31.212 --> 00:30:28.188
My point is that many are Lots; many are in the cities and they don't know it because they've become so complacent and lukewarm that they're in the midst of it, and it's going to take an intercessor to pull you out by the grace of God.

00:30:28.188 --> 00:30:32.379
That's why I'm a watchman.

00:30:32.379 --> 00:30:56.320
That's why I sit on my perch and I come on here to warn you that God said there will be a major shaking over America, but He's given you a window.

00:30:56.320 --> 00:31:07.731
There's something greater, something deeper to the meaning of this four-year window.

00:31:07.731 --> 00:31:08.870
It's big.

00:31:08.870 --> 00:31:17.659
This is the beginning of what I believe is the tribulation.

00:31:17.659 --> 00:31:28.925
He keeps speaking to me about this four-year window and I keep praying into it—a harvest of souls.

00:31:28.925 --> 00:31:37.491
Even Diana said, 'Brandon, I heard what you said about the harvest.

00:31:37.491 --> 00:31:57.159
' You said a financial crash will happen and then the harvest, a plague will happen, and all these things.

00:31:57.159 --> 00:31:59.312
But what brings the harvest?

00:32:09.142 --> 00:32:09.365
What is the trigger to the mechanism of the harvest?

00:32:09.365 --> 00:32:24.948
I saw a financial crisis throughout the whole world, I saw a plague, and I saw people running.

00:32:24.948 --> 00:32:29.504
What gets their attention?

00:32:29.504 --> 00:32:35.739
What shakes them out of their sleep?

00:32:35.739 --> 00:32:50.859
Touching their money, touching their circumstances; that's what shakes them out of it.

00:32:50.859 --> 00:32:55.839
I saw another major attack coming to America.

00:32:55.839 --> 00:32:57.880
I saw great shakings.

00:32:57.880 --> 00:33:00.480
I saw the enemy within again.

00:33:00.480 --> 00:33:15.977
I saw 'Red Dawn' again, praying over that, with a major uprising of these ants inside our country.

00:33:29.008 --> 00:33:29.217
I don't know what that is; I keep seeing it.

00:33:29.217 --> 00:33:30.888
So let's pray.

00:33:30.888 --> 00:33:57.820
I'm praying into the financial outpouring.

00:34:45.971 --> 00:34:52.039
We see the stock markets; we see what's happening.

00:34:52.039 --> 00:35:16.480
I told you, if they would go to that extent to eliminate JFK, how much more are they trying to bring down the dollar for the beast system, for a one-world order?

00:35:16.480 --> 00:35:23.836
Who is over all of this?

00:35:23.836 --> 00:35:34.567
Who's the boss?

00:35:34.567 --> 00:35:39.226
The devil.

00:35:39.226 --> 00:35:56.560
I told you I saw him strategically talking to major banking men and people in government.

00:35:56.560 --> 00:36:22.507
He was talking to them, the George Soroses, the Bill Gateses.

00:36:22.507 --> 00:36:30.269
He was influencing them, and they didn't realize it.

00:36:30.269 --> 00:36:51.611
I'm not going to say every one of them is having satanic practices, but I saw him influencing these men with great wealth.

00:37:02.900 --> 00:38:44.105
The Lord told me you do not get to that high level of wealth without a satanic agenda right now in the world; there's some demonic force feeding that because that's Satan's wheelhouse.

00:38:44.105 --> 00:39:11.960
So we're praying for the finances for the body of Christ, for the outpouring, for whatever the Holy Spirit wants us to pray for right now.

00:39:11.960 --> 00:39:24.335
We're going to pray for about 30 minutes unless the Holy Spirit leads us to go longer.

00:39:26.507 --> 00:39:41.629
We believe in the baptism of the Holy Spirit and we go into the throne boldly.

00:39:41.629 --> 00:39:55.783
I'm going to believe that God's going to show us things to come as a watchman today.

00:39:55.783 --> 00:40:12.564
Diana and I are going to do that, and if you see anything, tap me and let me know.

00:40:12.564 --> 00:40:17.203
Father, we thank You right now.

00:40:17.203 --> 00:40:22.299
We come before Your throne boldly.

00:40:22.299 --> 00:40:30.808
We take back what the enemy stolen from us.

00:40:30.808 --> 00:40:40.230
We believe, Father, for the 30, 60, and 100-fold return.

00:40:40.230 --> 00:40:53.180
We believe that everything we put our hands to will prosper.

00:40:53.180 --> 00:41:18.828
We take authority over the spirit of poverty and lack over our households, and we say, 'Thus far and no further!

00:41:18.828 --> 00:41:28.599
' You release our finances now in the name of Jesus.

00:41:28.599 --> 00:41:40.378
We call millions of dollars into the kingdom of God to flow through our hands.

00:41:40.378 --> 00:42:01.447
We believe that You're able to do exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:42:01.447 --> 00:42:20.405
We thank You, Lord, that the angels are going from the north, south, east, and west to bring the harvest in.

00:42:20.405 --> 00:42:39.869
We call in the harvest; we call in the lost, the ones in the very back field where it looks hopeless.

00:42:40.880 --> 00:42:46.000
You said give them one last call.

00:42:46.000 --> 00:42:58.480
We thank You, Lord, that there's a shaking to awaken.

00:42:58.480 --> 00:43:08.408
Every single one of them would have their eyes opened.

00:43:08.408 --> 00:43:27.780
We say in the name of Jesus, Satan, get your hands off of these unsaved loved ones!

00:43:27.780 --> 00:43:33.800
We call their eyes flooded with light.

00:43:33.800 --> 00:44:17.310
They would have a Damascus Road experience, a supernatural experience so they would understand there's a God that loves them and they would have a choice to serve the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:44:17.310 --> 00:44:26.857
You choose life or death, heaven or hell.

00:44:38.777 --> 00:44:39.274
I pray it's the right choice.

00:44:39.274 --> 00:45:11.026
Father, I thank You that they will not have any demonic interference to make that choice, that their eyes would be opened and they would see the lies from the pit of hell.

00:45:13.335 --> 00:45:20.167
It is a no-brainer to serve the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:45:44.674 --> 00:45:47.533
I thank You that their eyes would see how good You truly are, for You are good and Your mercy endures forever.

00:45:47.533 --> 00:46:03.515
Holy Spirit, work on their hearts today in the middle of their despair and agony.

00:46:03.515 --> 00:46:08.200
Draw them close to You, Father.

00:46:08.200 --> 00:46:25.027
We thank You for Your supernatural outpouring over the United States and around the world.

00:46:25.027 --> 00:46:34.102
We call forth revival from coast to coast.

00:46:34.102 --> 00:46:38.040
Holy Spirit, we yield ourselves.

00:46:38.040 --> 00:46:40.279
Flow through us.

00:46:40.279 --> 00:46:49.759
We ask You to show us that which is to come.

00:47:12.232 --> 00:47:12.683
I hear this: He said take communion.

00:47:12.683 --> 00:47:30.704
Father, we enter in by the blood, by this covenant.

00:47:30.704 --> 00:47:52.159
We thank You that we enter in by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of our testimony.

00:47:52.159 --> 00:47:55.870
We lift it up before You.

00:47:55.870 --> 00:48:25.333
He was wounded for our transgressions, He was bruised for our iniquities, the chastisement of our peace was upon Him, and with His stripes we are healed.

00:48:25.333 --> 00:48:45.846
We're going to walk in divine health and divine wealth.

00:48:45.846 --> 00:49:10.346
We take this body in the name of Jesus and thank You, Lord, that what You bore in Your body we need not bear in our own.

00:49:10.346 --> 00:49:24.079
We're healed and whole and well because You said it, Lord.

00:49:24.079 --> 00:49:36.970
Every good and perfect thing comes from the Father of Light.

00:49:36.970 --> 00:49:55.905
We take this blood in the name of Jesus and thank You for it.

00:49:55.905 --> 00:50:07.778
We apply the blood of Jesus over our sins.

00:50:07.778 --> 00:50:17.440
Now we enter into that throne by the blood.

00:50:17.440 --> 00:50:21.854
He says it's a dance.

00:50:26.495 --> 00:50:28.584
You don't rush the dance.

00:50:38.627 --> 00:50:42.879
It's a dance where one leads and one follows.

00:50:42.879 --> 00:50:47.493
He's leading, we follow.

00:50:48.418 --> 00:50:49.880
I see the ballroom.

00:50:49.880 --> 00:50:56.503
Don't be in a hurry; just let it flow.

00:50:57.413 --> 00:50:58.906
The symphony is beautiful.

00:50:58.906 --> 00:51:00.730
Intimacy is gentle.

00:51:00.730 --> 00:51:11.770
Get an inward image of what you're praying for today.

00:51:11.770 --> 00:51:19.950
See it in the eye and pray toward it.

00:51:19.950 --> 00:51:25.955
Don't just pray aimlessly; put your faith towards it.

00:51:25.955 --> 00:51:30.599
Visualize it inside and pray over it.

00:51:30.599 --> 00:51:39.754
Right now, we push for the finances of America, for the outpouring of finances.

00:51:39.754 --> 00:51:46.706
When you're praying in tongues, push it toward the outpouring.

00:51:46.706 --> 00:51:53.240
If we push together, we make much progress.

00:51:53.240 --> 00:52:04.280
We pray as a body and push as an army—focused, precision, pinpoint prayer.

00:52:04.280 --> 00:52:24.702
It's like lifting weights; we're grabbing and pulling that rope, moving stones out of the way to clear the road together.

00:52:24.702 --> 00:52:31.008
We seek You first, Lord.

00:52:31.008 --> 00:52:43.780
Seek ye first the kingdom and all these things will be added unto us.

00:52:43.780 --> 00:52:49.229
Seek My face, He says.

00:52:49.229 --> 00:52:56.786
Sit in My lap today.

00:52:56.786 --> 00:52:59.408
Abide in Me.

00:52:59.408 --> 00:53:05.266
If you abide in Me and My words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done unto you.

00:53:05.266 --> 00:53:14.383
Don't be out of balance with the finances; be in balance with Me.

00:53:14.383 --> 00:53:22.040
Seek My face and you can have what's in My hand.

00:53:22.620 --> 00:53:25.935
I will open the doors.

00:53:25.935 --> 00:53:29.269
It's back to the dance.

00:53:29.269 --> 00:53:34.059
As He leads, we follow.

00:53:34.059 --> 00:53:39.300
We will not get out of step.

00:53:39.300 --> 00:53:44.240
There's intimacy in the seeking.

00:53:44.240 --> 00:53:49.000
It's seeking the face of God.

00:53:49.000 --> 00:54:08.380
Seek Me, and I will give all unto you as I see that you can handle it.

00:54:08.380 --> 00:54:28.110
As you go from glory to glory, some are bridled and can handle it, but there are many that can't.

00:54:28.110 --> 00:54:42.596
So I wait and I watch for the heart that is after Me.

00:54:42.596 --> 00:54:48.537
As the heart panteth for the water brooks, so does my soul longeth after You.

00:54:48.537 --> 00:54:55.079
In the seeking, you lose yourself in Him.

00:54:55.079 --> 00:54:58.480
Nothing else matters.

00:54:58.480 --> 00:55:05.880
That's when the transfer happens—when you're dead to self.

00:55:09.114 --> 00:55:14.154
Many seek the money, but He says lose yourself in Me.

00:55:14.154 --> 00:55:24.880
When you are dead to self, it's a fragrance of beauty to Me.

00:55:24.880 --> 00:55:26.900
There's no faking death.

00:55:26.900 --> 00:55:37.144
When I know that you're yielded, it keeps you on that straight and narrow.

00:55:37.144 --> 00:55:53.329
Many of you are not ready for this wealth transfer, which is why I have said only one percent.

00:55:53.329 --> 00:56:00.646
I must be first, and wealth is a tool.

00:56:00.646 --> 00:56:10.739
Many are out of balance, seeking money with a divided heart.

00:56:10.739 --> 00:56:20.230
I'll have all of you or none of this.

00:56:20.230 --> 00:56:28.040
Seek Me, and in this, I will give it to you.

00:56:28.040 --> 00:56:32.220
Losing yourself in My face today.

00:56:40.280 --> 00:56:46.800
I keep seeing that He's a jealous God who desires us to be on fire.

00:56:46.800 --> 00:56:59.680
Many are lukewarm, seeking money with ulterior motives, not falling in love with the King.

00:56:59.680 --> 00:57:15.252
He sees the church with one foot in the world and one foot over here.

00:57:28.069 --> 00:57:28.554
I desire for you to have all of it.

00:57:31.028 --> 00:57:39.119
As you die to self, you will be entrusted with greater wealth.

00:57:39.119 --> 00:57:43.319
But you're running out of time.

00:57:43.319 --> 00:57:47.720
There will be levels of wealth.

00:57:47.720 --> 00:58:09.760
Many will stay down here and eat crumbs, but many will go up here and flow, funneling the crumbs.

00:58:09.760 --> 00:58:15.856
It's a process of keeping your lamps full.

00:58:23.199 --> 00:58:27.040
He is a holy God and will not allow this.

00:58:30.320 --> 00:58:34.102
He sees the intent of man.

00:58:35.004 --> 00:59:03.400
I will give you hidden treasures, riches stored in secret places, so that you may know that I am the Lord, the God of Israel, who summons you by name.

00:59:11.956 --> 00:59:12.192
The greater wealth transfer is a trusted thing.

00:59:12.192 --> 00:59:26.920
As you lose yourself in Him, He will show you the hidden treasures of Isaiah 45.

00:59:26.920 --> 00:59:40.440
Once you touch that hem, all the earthly stuff—the cars, the houses—nothing else matters but the glory.

00:59:46.488 --> 00:59:48.333
I am the Lord, and there is no other.

00:59:48.333 --> 00:59:56.172
Money is not your God.

00:59:59.753 --> 01:00:09.270
I form the light and create darkness; I bring prosperity and create disaster.

01:00:17.599 --> 01:00:18.079
I, the Lord, do all these things.

01:00:18.079 --> 01:00:27.266
Money is a tool, but I will not share My place.

01:00:27.266 --> 01:00:48.680
It's like the spoiled rich kid who loves on their dad just to get the keys to the car.

01:00:48.680 --> 01:00:57.822
He sees the motive of the heart.

01:00:57.822 --> 01:01:08.084
That's why He said only one percent—they've lost themselves in Me.

01:01:11.485 --> 01:01:17.280
It took the dance of the last many years.

01:01:17.720 --> 01:01:26.976
You cannot fake death; the odor gives it away.

01:01:30.483 --> 01:01:46.059
A person who is ready is a fragrance at the altar.

01:01:57.376 --> 01:02:24.360
I saw many in this vision grabbing fragments off the ground from the ones who were dead, funneling it down because they didn't care about it; all they cared about was Him.

01:02:24.360 --> 01:02:32.702
They were the main distributors because their eyes never broke eye contact with Him.

01:02:32.702 --> 01:02:36.044
They were glowing with the glory.

01:02:36.044 --> 01:03:00.232
As they kept their eyes on the throne, the finances flowed because they were no longer looking to finances to fill their joy cup.

01:03:00.968 --> 01:03:04.539
All I need is Him.

01:03:04.539 --> 01:03:14.433
He doesn't care if you have houses or cars, as long as they don't have you.

01:03:14.433 --> 01:03:23.279
He is a jealous God that wants all of us.

01:03:23.279 --> 01:03:28.599
He doesn't want your leftovers.

01:03:28.599 --> 01:03:32.610
Give Him your first.

01:03:32.610 --> 01:03:37.120
Don't give Him old, tired days.

01:03:37.120 --> 01:03:43.480
Relationship is maintaining that connection all day long.

01:03:58.079 --> 01:03:58.439
I pray this video blessed you.

01:04:09.295 --> 01:04:09.690
I appreciate the vision the Lord showed me.

01:04:18.943 --> 01:04:19.567
I give You all the glory, Father.

01:04:19.567 --> 01:04:37.085
Thank You for the correction and guidance.

01:04:37.085 --> 01:04:49.680
Thank You that You love me enough to rebuke me.

01:04:49.680 --> 01:04:57.659
Spank me, Lord, so that I would be better.

01:05:11.920 --> 01:05:16.191
We love You and praise You.

01:05:16.191 --> 01:05:22.080
Thank You for Isaiah 45.

01:05:30.204 --> 01:05:32.427
We will seek You and find You.

01:05:32.427 --> 01:05:43.123
Whatever You desire, we lose ourselves in You.

01:05:43.906 --> 01:05:46.905
You lead, we follow.

01:05:54.687 --> 01:06:03.698
I feel the presence of the Lord so strong.

01:06:03.698 --> 01:06:20.453
Jesus is wonderful.

01:06:20.453 --> 01:06:35.540
He said, 'Don't get in a rush, don't push it; dance.

01:06:35.540 --> 01:06:54.640
' He was rebuking me because I try to rush.

01:06:54.640 --> 01:07:09.495
No, dance, Brandon, just be at peace.

01:07:37.773 --> 01:07:38.320
Sit at My feet.

01:07:38.320 --> 01:08:29.105
I'll take these treasures and use them for the rest of my life.

01:08:29.105 --> 01:08:33.693
These are moments for me.

01:08:36.320 --> 01:08:37.759
We bless you all.

01:08:37.759 --> 01:08:45.119
Subscribe, click the notification bell, and comment something nice.

01:08:45.119 --> 01:08:51.000
Click like and thank you; it helps the algorithm.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
We'll never ask you for anything.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
Jesus Christ is coming back for a glorious church without spot or wrinkle.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
You're part of the remnant.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Focus on Him.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
Lose yourself in Him, and He'll give you everything.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
I want to be a person used by You, Father.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
We always humble ourselves before You.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
I decrease so that You increase.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
Thank You for the opportunity to worship You.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
In the presence of Jehovah God Almighty, troubles vanish and hearts are mended.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
We worship You, Father.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
If I could just sit with You a while...

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
We bless you today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
We'll see you again tomorrow.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Jesus loves you so much.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
God bless you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
